---
title: Sweet Potato Coconut Dal With King Prawns with Dukkah Salsa and Cheat's Chapati
description: Sri Lanka is often called the 'Resplendent Isle' and we can see why. Just have a taste of this dal recipe that Mimi came up with! Sweet potato marries beautifully with coconut milk and lentils cook down to a seductive softness, all the better to absorb those lovely spices.
